665
00:57:05,560 --> 00:57:07,590
- 真是好笑  - 泡利…
- Youse funny, or what? - Hey, Paulie?...

666
00:57:12,710 --> 00:57:15,610
喂，靠边停车好吗？我要放水
Hey, pull over, will you? I gotta take a leak.

667
00:57:57,330 --> 00:57:58,560
留下枪
Leave the gun.

668
00:57:59,070 --> 00:58:00,760
拿上坎诺里煎饼卷
Take the cannoli.

669
00:58:18,280 --> 00:58:21,850
喂，麦克…喂，麦基…
Hey, Mike! Hey, Mickey!

670
00:58:23,280 --> 00:58:24,140
在
Yeah?

671
00:58:24,150 --> 00:58:26,050
有电话找你
You're wanted on the telephone.

672
00:58:31,460 --> 00:58:33,860
- 是谁？  - 是个女孩
- Who is it? - It's some girl.

673
00:58:38,000 --> 00:58:40,470
- 你好，凯伊  - 你父亲还好吗？
Hello, Kay?how's your father?

674
00:58:40,580 --> 00:58:43,150
他很好，他能挺过来
He's good. He's gonna make it.

675
00:58:43,180 --> 00:58:44,630
我爱你
I love you.

676
00:58:46,220 --> 00:58:48,060
我爱你
I love you.

677
00:58:48,820 --> 00:58:51,270
- 迈克尔？  - 是，我知道
- Michael? - Yeah, I know.

678
00:58:51,430 --> 00:58:53,150
告诉我你爱我
Tell me you love me.

679
00:58:53,160 --> 00:58:54,450
我不能说
I can't talk.

680
00:58:54,460 --> 00:58:56,310
你不能说吗？
Can't you say it?

681
00:58:57,450 --> 00:58:59,310
我们今晚见
Yeah, I'll see you tonight.

682
00:59:00,280 --> 00:59:03,360
喂，麦基，你干嘛不告诉那好姑娘你爱她？
Hey, Mickey, why don't you tell that nice girl you love her?

683
00:59:03,370 --> 00:59:05,260
我全心全意爱你
I love you with all o' my heart!

684
00:59:05,270 --> 00:59:08,420
要是我不能快点再见到你，我会死的
If I don't see you again a-soon, I'm-a gonna die!

685
00:59:09,050 --> 00:59:10,900
过来，孩子，学点东西
Come over here, kid. Learn somethin'.

686
00:59:11,030 --> 00:59:14,020
你永远不知道，有一天你也许得给20个男人做饭
You never know, you might have to cook for 20 guys someday.

687
00:59:14,210 --> 00:59:17,900
看着，你开始先倒点油，然后炸大蒜
You see? You start out with a little bit of oil. Then you fry some garlic.

688
00:59:18,210 --> 00:59:21,020
然后扔进几个西红柿，番茄酱
Then you throw in some tomatoes, some tomato paste.

689
00:59:21,040 --> 00:59:23,310
你得炒一下，让它别粘锅
You fry it. You make sure it doesn't stick.

690
00:59:23,620 --> 00:59:27,530
煮开了之后，加入香肠及肉丸
When you got it to a boil, you shove in all your sausage and meatballs.

691
00:59:29,500 --> 00:59:31,440
再加一点点酒
And a little bit of wine.

692
00:59:34,880 --> 00:59:38,290
以及…一点点糖
And a little bit of sugar.

693
00:59:38,730 --> 00:59:39,560
那是我的秘方
And that's my trick.

694
00:59:39,570 --> 00:59:40,820
你别说废话了
Why don't you cut the crap?

695
00:59:40,830 --> 00:59:42,860
我有更重要的事要让你去做
I got more important things for you to do.

696
00:59:43,040 --> 00:59:43,950
泡利怎么样？
How's Paulie?

697
00:59:43,960 --> 00:59:45,690
哦，泡利，你再也见不到他了
Oh Paulie, won't see him no more.

698
00:59:47,430 --> 00:59:48,310
你要去哪里？
Where you going?

699
00:59:48,980 --> 00:59:49,810
到城里去
To the city.

700
00:59:50,350 --> 00:59:51,680
派几个保镖跟他一起去
Send some bodyguards with him.

701
00:59:51,710 --> 00:59:53,110
- 噢，我只是去医院看爸爸  - 我不管
- I'm just going to see Pop. - Never mind.

702
00:59:53,120 --> 00:59:53,940
派人跟他一起去
Send somebody with him.

703
00:59:53,960 --> 00:59:56,620
他不会有事的 索洛佐知道他是"平民"
He'll be all right. Sollozzo knows he's a civilian.

704
00:59:57,020 --> 00:59:59,480
- 好吧，小心点  - 是，长官
- All right. Be careful, huh? - Yes, sir.

705
01:00:02,280 --> 01:00:04,130
还是派人跟着他
Send somebody with him anyway.

706
01:00:33,100 --> 01:00:34,210
我得走了
I have to go.

707
01:00:34,730 --> 01:00:36,210
我能跟你一起去吗？
Can I go with you?

708
01:00:37,450 --> 01:00:39,910
不行，凯伊，那里会有探员
No, Kay. There's gonna be detectives there.

709
01:00:40,450 --> 01:00:41,510
媒体的人
People from the press.

710
01:00:42,230 --> 01:00:44,460
我搭出租车去
I'll ride in a cab.

711
01:00:46,650 --> 01:00:48,540
我不想要你卷进来
I don't want you to get involved.

712
01:00:52,080 --> 01:00:54,180
我何时能再见你？
When will I see you again?

713
01:01:00,540 --> 01:01:02,520
回新罕布什尔去
Go back to New Hampshire...

714
01:01:02,910 --> 01:01:05,390
我打电话去你父母家找你
and I'll call you at your parents' house.

715
01:01:06,540 --> 01:01:08,820
我何时才能再见你，迈克尔？
When will I see you again, Michael?

716
01:01:10,400 --> 01:01:11,890
我不知道
I don't know.

717
01:03:23,410 --> 01:03:24,810
你在这里干什么？
What are you doing here?

718
01:03:25,120 --> 01:03:27,150
这时候你不该来
You're not supposed to be here now.

719
01:03:27,370 --> 01:03:28,540
我是迈克尔・柯利昂尼
I'm Michael Corleone.

720
01:03:28,630 --> 01:03:30,180
这是我父亲
This is my father.

721
01:03:31,030 --> 01:03:33,470
这里没人，守卫人员都怎么了？
There's nobody here. What happened to the guards?

722
01:03:33,840 --> 01:03:38,430
你父亲访客太多，他们妨碍了医院的作业
Your father just had too many visitors. They interfered with hospital service.

723
01:03:38,790 --> 01:03:41,940
警察大概10分钟前要他们离开了
The police made them leave about ten minutes ago.

724
01:03:46,740 --> 01:03:51,190
请给我接长滩45620
Get me Long Beach 4-5-6-2-0, please.

725
01:03:53,250 --> 01:03:56,150
护士，等一下，待会儿
Nurse, wait a minute. Stay here.

726
01:03:59,550 --> 01:04:01,830
- 桑尼，是迈克尔，我在医院  - 哦
- Sonny, Michael. I'm at the hospital. - Yes

727
01:04:01,850 --> 01:04:03,710
听着，我来晚了，这里没有人
Listen. I got here late. There's nobody here.

728
01:04:03,720 --> 01:04:04,600
什么？没人？
What? Nobody?

729
01:04:04,610 --> 01:04:07,740
没人，泰西欧的人不在，没有探员，没有人
Nobody. No Tessio's men, no detectives, nobody.

730
01:04:07,910 --> 01:04:08,900
就爸爸一个人
Pop is all alone.

731
01:04:08,920 --> 01:04:10,540
别惊慌，我们会派人去
Don't panic. We'll send somebody.

732
01:04:10,550 --> 01:04:11,630
我不会惊慌
I won't panic.

733
01:04:12,920 --> 01:04:15,630
我很抱歉，但你必须离开了
I'm sorry, but you will have to leave.

734
01:04:18,480 --> 01:04:21,240
你和我要把我父亲移到另一个房间
You and I are gonna move my father to another room.

735
01:04:21,280 --> 01:04:24,410
现在你是否卸下这些管子，这样我们能把病床挪出去
Can you disconnect those tubes so we can move the bed out?

736
01:04:24,420 --> 01:04:25,730
那绝对不行
That's out of the question.

737
01:04:26,020 --> 01:04:27,530
你认识我父亲吗？
Do you know my father?

738
01:04:28,040 --> 01:04:29,660
有人正要来杀他
Men are coming here to kill him.

739
01:04:30,330 --> 01:04:31,460
你懂吗？
You understand?

740
01:04:32,460 --> 01:04:34,390
现在请你帮我忙
Now, help me, please.

741
01:05:51,300 --> 01:05:52,110
你是谁？
Who are you?

742
01:05:52,520 --> 01:05:55,210
我是恩佐，那个糕饼师
I am Enzo-- the baker.

743
01:05:56,120 --> 01:05:57,570
- 你还记得我吧？  - 恩佐
- You remember me? - Enzo?

744
01:05:57,620 --> 01:05:58,500
是的，恩佐
Yes, Enzo.

745
01:05:58,510 --> 01:06:00,520
你最好离开这里，恩佐，这里会有麻烦
You better get out of here, Enzo. There's gonna be trouble.

746
01:06:01,500 --> 01:06:04,010
要是有麻烦，我留在这帮你
If there is trouble, I stay here to help you--

747
01:06:04,020 --> 01:06:06,510
为了你父亲 为了你父亲
For your father. For your father.

748
01:06:07,530 --> 01:06:09,010
好吧，听我说
All right, listen.

749
01:06:09,400 --> 01:06:12,300
到外面等我，医院前面，好吗？
Wait for me outside, in front of the hospital. All right?

750
01:06:12,310 --> 01:06:14,010
我马上出来，快去
I'll be out in a minute. Go ahead.

751
01:06:14,030 --> 01:06:16,250
好的
Okay.

752
01:06:28,290 --> 01:06:30,440
好好休息吧，爸
Just lie here, Pop.

753
01:06:30,720 --> 01:06:32,960
现在我来照顾你
I'll take care of you now.

754
01:06:33,890 --> 01:06:35,250
现在我跟你一起了
I'm with you now.

755
01:06:37,540 --> 01:06:38,560
我跟你一起
I'm with you.

756
01:07:14,610 --> 01:07:15,990
扔掉这个
Get rid of these.

757
01:07:16,070 --> 01:07:17,310
过来
Come here.

758
01:07:17,820 --> 01:07:20,020
把手放在口袋里就像你有把枪
Put your hand in your pocket like you have a gun.

759
01:07:20,600 --> 01:07:22,060
你不会有事的
You'll be all right.

760
01:07:28,200 --> 01:07:29,310
你没事的
You'll be okay.

761
01:08:13,610 --> 01:08:15,420
你做的很好
You did good.

762
01:09:03,800 --> 01:09:05,880
我以为把你们这帮意大利打手都关起来了
I thought I got all you guinea hoods locked up.

763
01:09:05,920 --> 01:09:07,170
你在这里搞什么鬼？
What the hell are you doing here?

764
01:09:07,180 --> 01:09:10,080
守卫我父亲的人都怎么了，警监？
What happened to the men who were guarding my father, Captain?

765
01:09:10,230 --> 01:09:13,690
怎么，你这小混蛋，你算老几敢管我的事？
Why, you little punk. Who the hell are you telling me my business?

766
01:09:13,700 --> 01:09:15,820
我把那些人赶走了
I pulled them guys off of here.

767
01:09:15,830 --> 01:09:18,510
你马上走开，离开这医院
Now you get out of here and stay away from this hospital.

768
01:09:18,870 --> 01:09:22,120
我不会走，除非你派守卫到我父亲房间去
I'm not moving until you put some guards around my father's room.

769
01:09:22,520 --> 01:09:24,210
菲尔，把他带回去
Phil, take him in.

770
01:09:24,430 --> 01:09:25,950
这孩子是清白的，警监
The kid's clean, Captain.

771
01:09:25,960 --> 01:09:29,650
- 他是个战斗英雄，从未和…  -  该死的，我说了带他回去
- He's a war hero. He's never been busted-- - Goddamn it, I said take him in.

772
01:09:31,930 --> 01:09:35,010
“土耳其人”付你多少钱陷害我父亲，警监？
What's the Turk paying you to set up my father, Captain?

773
01:09:35,750 --> 01:09:37,880
抓牢他，让他站着
Take ahold of him. Stand him up.

774
01:09:38,330 --> 01:09:39,280
让他站稳了
Stand him up straight.

775
01:10:02,200 --> 01:10:04,320
我是柯利昂尼家的律师
I'm the attorney for the Corleone family.

776
01:10:04,330 --> 01:10:07,920
这些人是私家侦探，雇来保护维多・柯利昂尼的
These men are private detectives hired to protect Vito Corleone.

777
01:10:07,930 --> 01:10:10,350
他们持照携带火器
They're licensed to carry firearms.

778
01:10:10,360 --> 01:10:14,540
如果你干涉，明早你得面对一位法官并说明理由
If you interfere, you'll have to appear before a judge in the morning and show cause.

779
01:10:15,010 --> 01:10:17,030
好了，让他走
All right, let him go.

780
01:10:18,570 --> 01:10:20,110
来吧
Come on.

781
01:10:49,440 --> 01:10:51,470
这些新面孔是怎么回事？
What's with all the new faces?

782
01:10:51,480 --> 01:10:53,240
现在会需要他们的
Gonna need 'em now.

783
01:10:53,390 --> 01:10:56,060
经过医院的事之后，桑尼气疯了
After the hospital thing, Sonny got mad.

784
01:10:56,470 --> 01:10:59,880
我们今早四点干掉了布鲁诺・塔塔利亚
We hit Bruno Tattaglia at 4:00 this morning.

785
01:11:00,550 --> 01:11:02,570
老天爷
Jesus Christ.

786
01:11:09,490 --> 01:11:11,770
这里看起来像是座要塞
Looks like a fortress around here.

787
01:11:13,710 --> 01:11:15,630
（意大利语）

788
01:11:16,310 --> 01:11:19,330
100个雇佣枪手在街头，一天24小时
A hundred button men on the street, 24 hours a day.

789
01:11:19,340 --> 01:11:23,050
那土耳其人敢露出一根毛就死定了，相信我
That Turk shows one hair on his ass, he's dead. Believe me.

790
01:11:25,170 --> 01:11:27,840
迈克尔，过来，让我看看你
Hey, Michael, come here. Let me look at you.

791
01:11:31,210 --> 01:11:34,220
你样子好看，挺好看，漂亮极了
You look beautiful. Just beautiful. You're gorgeous.

792
01:11:34,310 --> 01:11:35,620
喂，听听这个
Hey, listen to this.

793
01:11:35,630 --> 01:11:37,320
那“土耳其人”，他想谈判
The Turk, he wants to talk.

794
01:11:37,330 --> 01:11:39,740
想想那个狗娘养的有多紧张
Imagine the nerve on this son of a bitch.

795
01:11:40,100 --> 01:11:42,310
昨晚跟我们赌一把，今天他想面谈
Craps out last night, now he wants a meeting today.

796
01:11:42,400 --> 01:11:43,700
- 他怎么说？  - 他怎么说？
- What'd he say? - What did he say?

797
01:11:45,410 --> 01:11:47,690
他要我们派迈克尔去听取提议
He wants us to send Michael to hear the proposition.

798
01:11:47,700 --> 01:11:51,300
并保证 那条件好到我们不会拒绝
And the promise is that the deal is so good that we can't refuse.

799
01:11:51,310 --> 01:11:52,890
那布鲁诺・塔塔利亚呢？
What about Bruno Tattaglia?

800
01:11:52,900 --> 01:11:54,460
那是条件的一部分
That's part of the deal.

801
01:11:54,470 --> 01:11:56,620
布鲁诺抵消了他们对我父亲所做的
Bruno cancels out what they did to my father.

802
01:11:56,630 --> 01:11:58,490
桑尼，我们得听听他们怎么说
Sonny, we ought to hear what they have to say.

803
01:11:58,500 --> 01:12:02,110
不不，不要了，这次不要，Consigliere
No more. Not this time, Consigliere.

804
01:12:02,120 --> 01:12:05,710
不再和谈，不再讨论，不再上索洛佐的当
No more meetings, no discussions, no more Sollozzo tricks.

805
01:12:05,720 --> 01:12:07,730
你给他们一个信息：我要索洛佐
You give them one message-- I want Sollozzo.

806
01:12:07,740 --> 01:12:08,860
否则就是全面开战，我们去睡床垫
If not, it's all-out war. We go to the mattresses.

807
01:12:08,870 --> 01:12:10,130
桑尼，其它家族不会支持的
Sonny, the other families won't sit still for a war.

808
01:12:10,140 --> 01:12:12,920
- 那就叫他们把索洛佐交给我  - 桑尼，你父亲不爱听这话
- Then they hand me Sollozzo. - Your father wouldn't hear this.

809
01:12:12,930 --> 01:12:14,460
这是生意，不是个人恩怨
This is business, not personal.

810
01:12:14,470 --> 01:12:15,620
他们枪击我父亲…
They shot my father.

811
01:12:15,630 --> 01:12:19,460
即便枪击你父亲也是生意，不是私事，桑尼
Even shooting your father was business, not personal, Sonny.

812
01:12:19,650 --> 01:12:21,590
那么生意就不得不受损了，行吗？
Well, then business will have to suffer. All right?

813
01:12:21,600 --> 01:12:23,070
听着，帮我个忙，汤姆
And listen, do me a favor, Tom--

814
01:12:23,420 --> 01:12:25,400
别再建议如何修修补补
No more advice on how to patch things up.

815
01:12:25,410 --> 01:12:27,620
只要帮我赢，好吗？
Just help me win, please. All right?

816
01:12:33,900 --> 01:12:36,530
我查了这个麦克劳斯基警监，他打断麦克的下巴
I found out about this Captain McCluskey who broke Mike's jaw.

817
01:12:36,540 --> 01:12:37,830
他怎么样？
What about him?

818
01:12:37,840 --> 01:12:41,250
他绝对在索洛佐的工资名单上，而且拿钱很多
He's definitely on Sollozzo's payroll, and for big money.

819
01:12:41,970 --> 01:12:44,220
麦克劳斯基同意当索洛佐的保镖
McCluskey has agreed to be the Turk's bodyguard.

820
01:12:44,230 --> 01:12:46,260
你必须要了解，桑尼
What you have to understand, Sonny...

821
01:12:46,270 --> 01:12:50,030
当索洛佐有了这样的警卫，他就无懈可击了
is that while Sollozzo's being guarded like this,  he is invulnerable.

822
01:12:50,040 --> 01:12:53,810
从来没人射杀过纽约警官，从未
Nobody has ever gunned down a New York police captain. Never.

823
01:12:53,820 --> 01:12:55,070
那会是个大灾难
It would be disastrous.

824
01:12:55,080 --> 01:12:56,980
五大家族全都会追杀你，桑尼
All the five families would come after you, Sonny.

825
01:12:56,990 --> 01:12:59,840
柯利昂尼家族会被驱逐
The Corleone family would be outcast.

826
01:12:59,850 --> 01:13:03,740
即便是老头的政治保护都会找掩护躲起来
Even the old man's political protection would run for cover.

827
01:13:05,020 --> 01:13:06,820
所以我拜托你
So do me a favor.

828
01:13:07,330 --> 01:13:09,740
好好考虑这一点
Take this into consideration.

829
01:13:12,800 --> 01:13:14,640
好吧  我们等
All right, we'll wait.

830
01:13:20,080 --> 01:13:21,520
我们不能等
We can't wait.

831
01:13:22,180 --> 01:13:23,430
我们不能等
Can't wait.

832
01:13:24,300 --> 01:13:28,030
我不管索洛佐说什么条件，他会杀了爸爸，就这样
I don't care what Sollozzo says about a deal. He's gonna kill Pop. That's it.

833
01:13:28,280 --> 01:13:30,130
那是他的关键
That's the key for him.

834
01:13:30,250 --> 01:13:31,960
我们必须干掉索洛佐
We've got to get Sollozzo.

835
01:13:32,280 --> 01:13:33,760
麦克说得对
Mike is right.

836
01:13:34,440 --> 01:13:36,660
我来问问你
Let me ask you something first.

837
01:13:36,670 --> 01:13:38,600
这个麦克劳斯基呢？
What about this McCluskey?

838
01:13:39,400 --> 01:13:41,860
我们拿这个条子怎么办？
What do we do with this cop here?

839
01:13:46,360 --> 01:13:48,760
他们想跟我会面，对吧？
They want to have a meeting with me, right?

840
01:13:50,260 --> 01:13:55,500
那会是我、麦克劳斯基及索洛佐
It will be me...McCluskey and Sollozzo.

841
01:13:56,470 --> 01:13:58,530
我们来安排会面
Let's set the meeting.

842
01:14:00,720 --> 01:14:04,390
找我们的线人打听出在哪里举行
Get our informers to find out where it's going to be held.

843
01:14:06,280 --> 01:14:10,140
我们坚持要公共场所，一间酒吧，一家餐厅
We insist it's a public place-- a bar, a restaurant.

844
01:14:10,150 --> 01:14:14,760
某个人多的地方，这样我感觉安全
Someplace where there's people, so I feel safe.

845
01:14:16,650 --> 01:14:19,620
我跟他们一见面，他们就会搜我身，对吧？
They're gonna search me when I first meet them, right?

846
01:14:19,730 --> 01:14:22,150
所以我身上不能有武器
So I can't have a weapon on me then.

847
01:14:25,360 --> 01:14:28,040
但如果克里门萨能想出一个办法
But if Clemenza can figure a way...

848
01:14:28,150 --> 01:14:31,180
替我在那里布置下武器
to have a weapon planted there for me...

849
01:14:35,420 --> 01:14:37,560
那我就能杀了他们两个
then I'll kill them both.

850
01:14:49,600 --> 01:14:52,510
你要怎么做？乖乖的大学生
What are you gonna do? Nice college boy, huh?

851
01:14:52,520 --> 01:14:54,370
以前不想跟家族事务混在一起
Didn't want to get mixed up in the family business.

852
01:14:54,430 --> 01:14:55,860
现在你想干掉一个警监？
Now you want to gun down a police captain?

853
01:14:55,870 --> 01:14:58,190
为什么？因为他小小扇了你一耳光？
Why? 'Cause he slapped you in the face a little bit?

854
01:14:58,200 --> 01:14:59,410
你以为这是什么？军队吗？
What're you think? This is the army?

855
01:14:59,420 --> 01:15:00,660
在一哩以外开枪打他们？
where you shoot them a mile away?

856
01:15:00,680 --> 01:15:02,240
你必须离这么近，然后“砰”
You gotta get up close, like this and--

857
01:15:02,250 --> 01:15:04,630
你漂亮的常春藤名校服上溅满他们的脑浆
You blow their brains all over your nice Ivy League suit.

858
01:15:04,850 --> 01:15:05,510
- 过来  - 桑尼
- Come here.  - Sonny.

859
01:15:06,360 --> 01:15:08,030
你把这事当成私仇了
You're taking this very personal.

860
01:15:08,060 --> 01:15:11,570
汤姆，这是生意，而这位把它当私仇了
Tom, this is business, and this man is taking it very, very personal.

861
01:15:11,580 --> 01:15:14,060
不能杀条子是哪里来的说法？
Where does it say you can't kill a cop?

862
01:15:14,400 --> 01:15:15,970
- 好了，麦基  - 汤姆，等一下
- Come on, Mikey. - Tom, wait a minute.

863
01:15:15,980 --> 01:15:19,080
我说的这个条子，他跟毒品搅在一起
I'm talking about a cop that's mixed up in drugs.

864
01:15:19,090 --> 01:15:23,040
我说的是个不诚实的条子，不正当的条子
I'm talking about a dishonest cop, a crooked cop...

865
01:15:23,050 --> 01:15:26,210
跟犯罪集团混在一起，终于遭了报应
who got mixed up in the rackets and got what was coming to him.

866
01:15:26,740 --> 01:15:28,210
这是个精彩的故事
That's a terrific story.

867
01:15:28,460 --> 01:15:31,370
我们的工资单上有报社的人，对吧汤姆？
We have newspaper people on the payroll, don't we, Tom?

868
01:15:32,590 --> 01:15:34,440
他们也许会喜欢这种故事
They might like a story like that.

869
01:15:34,900 --> 01:15:37,090
他们也许会，只是也许
They might. They just might.

870
01:15:40,140 --> 01:15:44,390
这不是私仇，桑尼，纯粹是公事
It's not personal, Sonny. It's strictly business.

871
01:15:46,840 --> 01:15:48,310
它从没用过
It's as cold as they come.

872
01:15:48,630 --> 01:15:52,120
不可能追踪，所以不用担心指纹，麦克
Impossible to trace, so you don't worry about prints, Mike.

873
01:15:52,130 --> 01:15:55,010
我贴了特殊胶布在扳机和柄上
I put a special tape on the trigger and the butt.

874
01:15:55,170 --> 01:15:56,970
来，试试
Here. Try it.

875
01:16:08,540 --> 01:16:11,040
怎么？扳机太紧了？
What's the matter, the trigger too tight?

876
01:16:14,010 --> 01:16:16,170
- 哇，我的耳朵  - 对，我没处理枪声
- My ears. - Yeah, I left it noisy.

877
01:16:16,230 --> 01:16:20,250
这样就可以吓走多管闲事的旁观者
That way it scares any pain-in-the-ass innocent bystanders away.

878
01:16:21,130 --> 01:16:23,610
好了，你杀了他俩，现在你做什么？
All right, you shot them both. Now what do you do?

879
01:16:26,080 --> 01:16:28,360
坐下，吃完我的晚餐
Sit down, finish my dinner.

880
01:16:28,420 --> 01:16:30,070
好了，小子，别捣乱啦
Come on, kid. Don't fool around.

881
01:16:30,080 --> 01:16:33,670
就让你的手顺身侧垂下，让枪滑走
Just let your hand drop to your side and let the gun slip out.

882
01:16:33,680 --> 01:16:35,840
人人都会认为你还拿着它
Everybody will still think you got it.

883
01:16:35,850 --> 01:16:38,010
他们会盯着你的脸，麦克
They're gonna be staring at your face, Mike...

884
01:16:38,020 --> 01:16:41,040
所以快步离开那地方，但不要跑
so walk out of the place real fast, but you don't run.

885
01:16:41,230 --> 01:16:44,310
别直视任何人，但你也不要挪开目光
Don't look nobody directly in the eye, but don't look away, either.

886
01:16:44,920 --> 01:16:48,570
他们会被你吓坏，相信我，所以什么也不用担心
They're gonna be scared stiff of you, believe me...so don't worry about nothing.

887
01:16:50,300 --> 01:16:52,040
你看，你会全身而退的
You know, you're gonna turn out all right.

888
01:16:52,060 --> 01:16:54,640
你休个长假，去谁也不知道的地方
You take a long vacation, nobody knows where...

889
01:16:54,650 --> 01:16:56,450
而我们来收拾善后
and we're gonna catch the hell.

890
01:16:57,260 --> 01:16:58,960
你觉得情况会有多糟？
How bad do you think it's gonna be?

891
01:16:59,370 --> 01:17:01,050
相当他妈的糟糕
Pretty goddamn bad.

892
01:17:01,180 --> 01:17:04,150
可能其它所有家族会联合对付我们
Probably all the other families will line up against us.

893
01:17:04,340 --> 01:17:05,170
那也没关系
That's all right.

894
01:17:05,180 --> 01:17:08,710
这种事大概每隔5年会发生，或10年
These things gotta happen every five years or so. Ten years.

895
01:17:08,720 --> 01:17:10,090
有助于消除不和
Helps to get rid of the bad blood.

896
01:17:10,100 --> 01:17:12,430
从上次以来已有10年了
Been ten years since the last one.

897
01:17:12,880 --> 01:17:14,560
你看你得一开始就制止他们
You know you gotta stop them at the beginning...

898
01:17:14,610 --> 01:17:16,780
就像他们本该在慕尼黑制止希特勒
like they should have stopped Hitler at Munich.

899
01:17:16,790 --> 01:17:20,820
他们那次就不该让他逃过去，那是自找麻烦
They should have never let him get away with that. They was just asking for big trouble.

900
01:17:21,700 --> 01:17:22,990
知道吗，麦克
You know, Mike,

901
01:17:23,140 --> 01:17:26,100
我们都以你为荣…当战斗英雄什么的
we was all proud of you... being a hero and all.

902
01:17:26,410 --> 01:17:28,020
你父亲也是
Your father too.

903
01:18:06,200 --> 01:18:09,650
没有，一点线索没有，什么也没有
Nothing. Not a hint. Absolutely nothing.

904
01:18:10,590 --> 01:18:13,730
连索洛佐的人也不知道在会面哪里举行
Even Sollozzo's people don't know where the meeting will be held.

905
01:18:14,820 --> 01:18:16,590
我们有多少时间？
How much time do we have?

906
01:18:17,830 --> 01:18:20,550
一个半小时以后，他们在杰克丹普西餐厅前接你上车
pick you up in front of Jack Dempsey's in an hour and a half--

907
01:18:20,630 --> 01:18:22,310
正好一个半小时以后
exactly an hour and a half.

908
01:18:24,040 --> 01:18:26,670
我们可以派盯梢，看看最后去哪儿
We could put a tail on them, see how it turns out.

909
01:18:26,910 --> 01:18:29,540
索洛佐会在街上乱转 甩掉我们的人
Sollozzo'll lose our ass going around the block.

910
01:18:30,040 --> 01:18:31,710
谈判中间人呢？
What about the negotiator?

911
01:18:31,990 --> 01:18:34,810
他在我那里和我的手下玩皮纳克纸牌
He's over at my place playing pinochle with a couple of my men.

912
01:18:34,830 --> 01:18:36,560
他很高兴  我们在让他赢
He's happy. They're letting him win.

913
01:18:37,020 --> 01:18:38,330
这对麦克太冒险了
It's too much of a risk for Mike.

914
01:18:38,340 --> 01:18:39,870
也许我们该取消，桑尼
Maybe we ought to call it off, Sonny.

915
01:18:39,910 --> 01:18:43,520
那个中间人要一直玩牌等到麦克安然无恙回来才走
The negotiator keeps on playing cards until Mike's back safe and sound.

916
01:18:43,540 --> 01:18:45,890
那他干嘛不直接对车里不管什么人开火呢？
So why doesn't he just blast who's ever in the goddamn car?

917
01:18:45,960 --> 01:18:47,520
太危险了，他们会注意的
Too dangerous. They'll be looking for that.

918
01:18:47,530 --> 01:18:50,200
索洛佐也许根本就不在车上，桑尼
Sollozzo might not even be in the car, Sonny.

919
01:18:51,040 --> 01:18:52,630
我来接
I got it.

920
01:19:17,840 --> 01:19:19,610
布朗克斯的路易斯餐厅
Louis Restaurant in the Bronx.

921
01:19:20,130 --> 01:19:21,300
可靠吗？
Well, is it reliable?

922
01:19:21,310 --> 01:19:23,110
麦克劳斯基的分局里有我的人
That's my man in McCluskey's precinct.

923
01:19:23,410 --> 01:19:26,070
警监必须一天24小时待命
A police captain's got to be on call 24 hours a day.

924
01:19:26,080 --> 01:19:28,580
他八点到十点会去那里
He signed out at that number between 8:00 and 10:00.

925
01:19:29,210 --> 01:19:30,440
有谁知道那个地方？
Anybody know this joint?

926
01:19:30,450 --> 01:19:32,160
当然，我知道
Yeah, sure. I do.

927
01:19:32,860 --> 01:19:34,130
对我们太理想了
It's perfect for us.

928
01:19:34,140 --> 01:19:36,500
小型家庭餐厅，食物不错
A small family place, good food.

929
01:19:36,510 --> 01:19:39,230
大家各吃各的，太理想了
Everyone minds his business. It's perfect.

930
01:19:39,240 --> 01:19:42,270
彼得，他们那儿有个旧式马桶
Pete, they got an old-fashioned toilet--

931
01:19:42,280 --> 01:19:45,950
你知道就是水箱有吊链的那种
You know, the box and the chain thing.

932
01:19:47,180 --> 01:19:50,130
我们或许可把枪用胶带绑在那后面
We might be able to tape the gun behind it.

933
01:19:50,160 --> 01:19:51,150
好的
All right.

934
01:19:51,340 --> 01:19:54,310
麦克，你去餐厅
Mike, you go to the restaurant.

935
01:19:54,410 --> 01:19:56,660
你吃着谈上一会儿，要放松
You eat, you talk for a while, you relax.

936
01:19:56,860 --> 01:19:58,330
你让他们放松下来
You make them relax.

937
01:19:58,510 --> 01:20:00,790
然后你站起来，去解手
Then you get up and go take a leak.

938
01:20:00,940 --> 01:20:03,680
不，更好的是，你要求得到许可再去
No, better still, you ask for permission to go.

939
01:20:03,750 --> 01:20:05,590
等你回来，你就开枪
And when you come back, you come out blasting.

940
01:20:05,600 --> 01:20:08,510
不要心存侥幸，每人脑袋上来两枪
And don't take any chances. Two shots in the head apiece.

941
01:20:08,760 --> 01:20:12,790
好了，听着，我要一个好手，真正的好手去藏枪
Now, listen. I want somebody good-- and I mean very good-- to plant that gun.

942
01:20:12,800 --> 01:20:16,020
我不想我兄弟走出厕所手里只握着自己的老二，明白？
I don't want him coming out of that toilet with just his dick in his hands, all right?

943
01:20:16,180 --> 01:20:17,310
枪会在那里的
The gun will be there.

944
01:20:17,340 --> 01:20:21,420
好，听着，你开车送他，事后再接他回来
All right, listen. You drive him and you pick him up after the job.

945
01:20:21,730 --> 01:20:23,310
来吧，赶紧行动
Come on. Let's move.

946
01:20:29,210 --> 01:20:32,360
他有没有…告诉你完事就扔掉枪？
Did he tell you to drop the gun right away?

947
01:20:32,370 --> 01:20:34,260
有，上百万次了
Yeah, a million times.

948
01:20:37,740 --> 01:20:38,440
好了
Now

949
01:20:38,840 --> 01:20:43,000
你别忘了，每人头上两枪，一出厕所后就打
You don't forget-- two shots apiece in the head as soon as you come out the door.

950
01:20:43,510 --> 01:20:44,280
我们走
Let's go.

951
01:20:49,690 --> 01:20:52,330
你认为要多久我才能回家？
How long do you think it'll be before I can come back?

952
01:20:54,510 --> 01:20:56,230
至少得一年，麦克
At least a year, Mike.

953
01:20:56,440 --> 01:20:58,080
听着，我会协调妈妈那边…
Listen, I'll square with Mom

954
01:20:58,090 --> 01:21:01,450
你知道你走前不能去看她，还有…
you know you're not seeing her before you leave and...

955
01:21:02,690 --> 01:21:04,650
我会给你那女友送个消息
I'll get a message to that girlfriend

956
01:21:04,730 --> 01:21:06,710
等我觉得合适的时候
when I think the time is right.

957
01:21:12,460 --> 01:21:14,390
保重
Take care.

958
01:21:17,030 --> 01:21:19,310
- 再见，麦克  - 汤姆
- See you, Mike.  - Tom

959
01:21:51,240 --> 01:21:53,050
我很高兴你来了，麦克
I'm glad you came, Mike.

960
01:21:53,520 --> 01:21:55,470
我希望我们能摆平所有事情
I hope we can straighten everything out.

961
01:21:56,350 --> 01:21:59,710
我说这太可怕了，这完全不是我想要的发展
I mean this is terrible. It's not the way I wanted things to go at all.

962
01:21:59,870 --> 01:22:01,360
完全就不该发生的
It should have never happened.

963
01:22:01,370 --> 01:22:03,340
我想在今晚摆平所有事
I want to straighten everything out tonight.

964
01:22:03,370 --> 01:22:05,410
我不想要我父亲再受打扰
I don't want my father bothered anymore.

965
01:22:05,940 --> 01:22:06,910
他不会了，麦克
He won't be, Mike.

966
01:22:06,920 --> 01:22:09,310
我以我的孩子发誓不会
I swear on my children he won't.

967
01:22:10,170 --> 01:22:12,960
但我们谈的时候你得心态开放
But you got to keep an open mind when we talk.

968
01:22:13,460 --> 01:22:15,680
我是说，我希望你不像你哥哥那样热血
I mean I hope you're not a hothead like your brother Sonny.

969
01:22:15,690 --> 01:22:17,710
你没办法跟他谈正事
You can't talk business with him.

970
01:22:17,920 --> 01:22:19,390
(意大利语)

971
01:22:19,410 --> 01:22:21,470
呃，他是个好孩子
He's a good kid.

972
01:22:25,540 --> 01:22:27,840
那晚的事我很抱歉，麦克
I'm sorry about the other night, Mike.

973
01:22:29,170 --> 01:22:31,360
我得搜你身，转过来
I gotta frisk you, so turn around, huh?

974
01:22:31,660 --> 01:22:34,060
跪在椅子上，面向我
On your knees, facing me.

975
01:22:38,030 --> 01:22:41,070
我想我干这行已经嫌老了
I guess I'm getting too old for my job.

976
01:22:41,860 --> 01:22:43,520
太厌烦
Too grouchy.

977
01:22:44,290 --> 01:22:45,760
受不了别人的激怒
Can't stand the aggravation.

978
01:22:46,930 --> 01:22:48,210
你知道是怎么回事
You know how it is.

979
01:22:50,570 --> 01:22:51,740
他没武器
He's clean.

980
01:23:18,540 --> 01:23:19,830
我们要去新泽西？
We're going to New Jersey?

981
01:23:23,310 --> 01:23:24,630
也许
Maybe.

982
01:23:50,060 --> 01:23:51,420
干得好，卢
Nice work, Lou.

983
01:24:29,170 --> 01:24:30,910
这餐厅的意大利菜怎么样？
How's the Italian food in this restaurant?

984
01:24:31,340 --> 01:24:32,310
不错
Good.

985
01:24:32,460 --> 01:24:34,430
试试小牛肉，是城里最棒的
Try the veal. It's the best in the city.

986
01:24:34,640 --> 01:24:35,810
我就点它了
I'll have it.

987
01:24:37,630 --> 01:24:39,650
快[意大利语]

988
01:25:08,720 --> 01:25:10,390
好了[意大利语]

989
01:25:11,710 --> 01:25:14,110
我要跟麦克说意大利语
I'm gonna speak Italian to Mike.

990
01:25:14,420 --> 01:25:15,440
请便
Go ahead.

991
01:25:21,340 --> 01:25:23,820
- 我很抱歉  - 算了

992
01:25:26,840 --> 01:25:33,820
要知道，你父亲身上发生的事，是生意

993
01:25:34,340 --> 01:25:37,820
我很尊重你的父亲

994
01:25:37,940 --> 01:25:41,020
但你父亲的想法过时了

995
01:25:42,640 --> 01:25:47,020
你必须理解 我为什么做出那种事

996
01:25:47,310 --> 01:25:51,020
我理解这种事

997
01:25:51,510 --> 01:25:53,970
- 真的理解  - 是吗？

998
01:26:05,920 --> 01:26:08,810
现在我们不得不考虑

999
01:26:09,520 --> 01:26:11,870
你们跟塔塔利亚家族之间的事

1000
01:26:13,440 --> 01:26:17,110
我们必须想出办法 何去何从

1001
01:26:18,440 --> 01:26:23,210
（这里几句我没法翻译，没英语字幕了）

1002
01:26:23,740 --> 01:26:23,740
（这几句是我猜着翻译的）

1003
01:26:23,740 --> 01:26:25,110
