01:49:27,730 --> 01:49:33,470
(意大利语)

1193
01:53:06,850 --> 01:53:08,060
没想到你会来，凯伊
Weren't expecting you, Kay.

1194
01:53:08,780 --> 01:53:09,630
你应该先打个电话来
You should call.

1195
01:53:09,740 --> 01:53:11,290
没错，我打过
Yes, well, I have.

1196
01:53:11,380 --> 01:53:14,010
我是说，我试过写信和打电话
I mean I've tried writing and calling.

1197
01:53:14,260 --> 01:53:16,550
现在，我要和迈克尔联络
Now, I wanna reach Michael.

1198
01:53:16,740 --> 01:53:18,110
没人知道他在哪
Nobody knows where he is.

1199
01:53:18,210 --> 01:53:20,440
我们知道他没事，但仅此而已了
We know he's all right, but that's all.

1200
01:53:23,310 --> 01:53:24,270
那是怎么回事？
What was that?

1201
01:53:24,650 --> 01:53:27,380
那是一场事故，但没有人受伤
That's an accident. But nobody was hurt.

1202
01:53:27,810 --> 01:53:28,730
汤姆
Tom.

1203
01:53:29,740 --> 01:53:33,520
能不能请你 把这封信交给迈克尔？拜托了
Would you give this letter to Michael, please? Please?

1204
01:53:33,690 --> 01:53:34,970
如果我接受了
if I accepted that

1205
01:53:35,630 --> 01:53:38,970
在法庭上，它就可以证实我知道他在哪里
in a court of law they could prove I have knowledge of his whereabouts.

1206
01:53:39,480 --> 01:53:41,750
耐心点，凯伊，他会与你联络的，好吗？
Just be patient, Kay. He'll get in touch with you.

1207
01:53:41,760 --> 01:53:45,340
我让我的出租车走了，我能否进去另叫一辆？
I let my cab go. Can I come in to call another one pleas?

1208
01:53:45,640 --> 01:53:47,620
来吧  对不起  来吧
Come on. I'm sorry. Come on.

1209
01:54:08,540 --> 01:54:09,810
卡洛在吗？
Is Carlo there?

1210
01:54:10,220 --> 01:54:12,740
- 你是哪位？  - 我是卡洛的一个朋友
- Who's this? - This is a friend of Carlo's.

1211
01:54:12,750 --> 01:54:16,310
你能不能告诉他 我今晚晚些才有空？
Would you tell him that I can't make it tonight until later?

1212
01:54:21,910 --> 01:54:22,930
婊子
Bitch.

1213
01:54:25,230 --> 01:54:27,930
- 晚餐在桌上  - 我还不饿
- Dinner's on the table. - I'm not hungry yet.

1214
01:54:27,980 --> 01:54:30,630
- 晚餐在桌上快凉了  - 我晚点再吃
- Your food is on the table. It's getting cold. - I'll eat out later.

1215
01:54:31,450 --> 01:54:33,240
你刚叫我给你做晚饭的
You just told me to make you dinner.

1216
01:54:33,250 --> 01:54:37,900
- 喂，操你妈[意大利语]  - 我才操你妈[意大利语]
-Hey, vaffanculo, eh?  -I'll vaffanculo you!

1217
01:54:42,690 --> 01:54:45,420
她这嘴真脏，这意大利小妞
She has a filthy mouth, this little guinea brat.

1218
01:54:49,510 --> 01:54:53,510
对了，全砸烂，你这宠坏了的意大利小妞，全砸掉
That's it. Break it all, you spoiled guinea brat. Break it all!

1219
01:55:02,680 --> 01:55:06,640
你怎么不把那个妓女带回家吃晚饭？
Why don't you bring your whore home for dinner?

1220
01:55:07,010 --> 01:55:09,150
也许我会的，有何不可？
Maybe I will. Why not?

1221
01:55:15,230 --> 01:55:16,530
给我清干净
Now clean it up!

1222
01:55:16,740 --> 01:55:19,070
我才不要
Like hell I will!

1223
01:55:19,080 --> 01:55:21,450
清干净，你这宠坏了的意大利小妞
Clean it up, you guinea spoiled brat!

1224
01:55:21,460 --> 01:55:25,680
清干净，清干净，我说清干净
Clean it up! Clean it up! I said clean it up!

1225
01:55:27,720 --> 01:55:29,610
清干净
Clean it up!

1226
01:55:30,210 --> 01:55:31,120
不
No!

1227
01:55:31,140 --> 01:55:33,310
清干净，你这婊子养的
Clean it up! You son of a bitch!

1228
01:55:34,960 --> 01:55:35,810
清理掉
Clean it!

1229
01:55:36,910 --> 01:55:38,190
清干净
Clean it up!

1230
01:55:38,510 --> 01:55:41,340
好，来啊，杀我，当凶手啊，像你爸一样
Come on, now! Kill me! Be a murderer like your father!

1231
01:55:41,350 --> 01:55:43,840
- 来吧，你们姓柯利昂尼的全是凶手  - 我恨你
- Come on, all you Corleones are murderers! - I hate you!

1232
01:55:43,850 --> 01:55:45,910
- 来啊  - 我要杀了你
- Come on! - I'll kill you!

1233
01:55:45,920 --> 01:55:49,820
来啊，杀了我，给我滚
Kill me! Get up! Get out of here!

1234
01:55:49,840 --> 01:55:53,310
- 我恨你   - 好，赶紧的，我要杀你了
- I hate you! - Now, go ahead. now I'll kill you.

1235
01:55:53,440 --> 01:55:55,110
你这意大利小妞
You guinea brat, you.

1236
01:55:55,130 --> 01:55:57,060
滚出来
Get out here!

1237
01:56:06,490 --> 01:56:07,910
康妮，怎么回事？
Connie, what's the matter?

1238
01:56:08,110 --> 01:56:10,210
我听不见你说的，什么事？
I can't hear you. What is it?

1239
01:56:10,570 --> 01:56:13,520
康妮，说大声点，孩子在哭
Connie, talk louder. The baby's crying.

1240
01:56:13,730 --> 01:56:17,310
桑提诺，我听不懂，我不明白
Santino, I can't understand-- I don't know. I don't understand.

1241
01:56:17,900 --> 01:56:19,180
什么事，康妮？
Yeah, Connie.

1242
01:56:24,710 --> 01:56:26,310
听着，你在那里等着
Listen, you wait there.

1243
01:56:29,060 --> 01:56:31,320
不，你在那等着就好了
No, you just wait there.

1244
01:56:33,880 --> 01:56:35,350
那婊子养的
That son of a bitch.

1245
01:56:36,460 --> 01:56:37,650
婊子养的
Son of a bitch.

1246
01:56:37,860 --> 01:56:39,890
- 桑尼，怎么了？  - 王八蛋
- Sonny, what's the matter?

1247
01:56:43,440 --> 01:56:46,630
快他妈开门 站起来
Open the goddamn gate. Get off your ass.

1248
01:56:54,450 --> 01:56:55,370
桑尼
Sonny.

1249
01:57:01,870 --> 01:57:02,530
让开！
Get out!

1250
01:57:02,540 --> 01:57:03,530
桑尼，桑尼，下来
Sonny. Sonny, come on!

1251
01:57:03,540 --> 01:57:05,130
滚开
Get out of here!

1252
01:57:05,540 --> 01:57:07,520
跟着他，快点
Go after him. Go on.

1253
01:57:36,930 --> 01:57:37,870
王八蛋
Son of a bitch.

1254
01:57:38,230 --> 01:57:40,630
赶紧，赶紧…
Come on! Come on!

1255
01:59:27,740 --> 01:59:29,320
给我一口
Give me a drop.

1256
01:59:37,960 --> 01:59:40,940
我妻子在楼上哭
My wife is crying upstairs.

1257
01:59:42,710 --> 01:59:45,430
我听见车子开到家里来
I hear cars coming to the house.

1258
01:59:49,720 --> 01:59:51,310
我的Consigliere
Consigliere of mine...

1259
01:59:53,150 --> 01:59:56,310
我想你应该告诉你的唐，人人都知道的那件事了
I think you should tell your Don what everyone seems to know.

1260
01:59:56,500 --> 01:59:58,350
我什么也没告诉妈妈
I didn't tell Mama anything.

1261
01:59:59,810 --> 02:00:03,310
我刚才正要去叫醒你并告诉你
I was about to come up and wake you just now and tell you.

1262
02:00:06,480 --> 02:00:08,640
但你需要先喝一杯
But you needed a drink first.

1263
02:00:11,060 --> 02:00:11,940
是
Ya.

1264
02:00:15,690 --> 02:00:17,970
现在你喝过酒了
Now you've had your drink.

1265
02:00:23,610 --> 02:00:26,350
他们在堤道上枪击了桑尼
They shot Sonny on the causeway.

1266
02:00:26,740 --> 02:00:28,020
他死了
He's dead.

1267
02:00:45,010 --> 02:00:48,120
我不要做调查
I want no inquiries made.

1268
02:00:51,610 --> 02:00:54,360
我不要复仇行动
I want no acts of vengeance.

1269
02:00:55,690 --> 02:00:57,930
我要你安排一次会议
I want you to arrange a meeting...

1270
02:00:59,560 --> 02:01:02,140
与五大家族的首领
with the heads of the five families.

1271
02:01:04,290 --> 02:01:06,870
这场战争现在停止
This war stops now.

1272
02:01:28,120 --> 02:01:30,490
打电话给博纳塞拉
Call Bonasera.

1273
02:01:30,850 --> 02:01:32,650
我们现在需要他了
We need him now.

1274
02:01:45,280 --> 02:01:46,740
我是汤姆・黑根
This is Tom Hagen...

1275
02:01:46,750 --> 02:01:49,860
按维多・柯利昂尼的要求 打这个电话
calling for Vito Corleone, at his request.

1276
02:01:50,400 --> 02:01:52,710
你欠你的唐一次服务
Now, you owe your Don a service.

1277
02:01:53,000 --> 02:01:56,310
他毫不怀疑你会回报他
he has no doubt that you will repay it.

1278
02:01:56,560 --> 02:01:59,330
他在一小时后会到你的殡仪馆去
Now, he will be at your funeral parlor in one hour.

1279
02:01:59,350 --> 02:02:00,960
去那里迎接他
Be there to greet him.

1280
02:02:22,130 --> 02:02:24,200
我的朋友
Well, my friend...

1281
02:02:24,560 --> 02:02:27,030
你准备好为我服务了吗？
are you ready to do me this service?

1282
02:02:27,040 --> 02:02:27,810
是的
Yes.

1283
02:02:28,740 --> 02:02:30,810
你要我做什么？
What do you want me to do?

1284
02:02:38,420 --> 02:02:44,390
我要你用上你全部力量，全部技能
I want you to use all your powers... and all your skills.

1285
02:02:47,190 --> 02:02:50,770
我不要他母亲看到他这个样子
I don't want his mother to see him this way.

1286
02:03:06,280 --> 02:03:09,300
看看他们是怎么残害了我的孩子
Look how they massacred my boy.

1287
02:03:39,710 --> 02:03:41,660
教你英语安全一点

1288
02:03:41,990 --> 02:03:43,310
我会英语

1289
02:03:43,320 --> 02:03:45,430
星期一、星期二、星期三
Monday, Tuesday, Thursday...

1290
02:03:45,440 --> 02:03:48,460
星期四、星期五、星期日、星期六
Wednesday, Friday, Sunday, Saturday

1291
02:03:48,470 --> 02:03:50,150
- 哦，好极了  - 快来快来
- Bravo! - Come on, come on.

1292
02:03:56,170 --> 02:03:57,810
欢迎，唐・汤玛西诺

1293
02:03:58,830 --> 02:04:00,010
巴勒莫那边怎么样？

1294
02:04:04,330 --> 02:04:06,340
你好，唐・汤玛西诺

1295
02:04:06,770 --> 02:04:10,420
迈克尔在教我开车

1296
02:04:10,440 --> 02:04:12,840
来，我开给你看

1297
02:04:12,880 --> 02:04:14,760
巴勒莫那边怎么样？

1298
02:04:15,740 --> 02:04:18,750
年轻人不再尊重任何事了

1299
02:04:18,910 --> 02:04:22,060
时代越变越糟

1300
02:04:23,810 --> 02:04:31,280
这地方对你己变得太危险了

1301
02:04:31,290 --> 02:04:39,170
我要你搬到锡拉库萨附近的一座别墅去，马上

1302
02:04:41,860 --> 02:04:43,520
有什么不对了?

1303
02:04:44,630 --> 02:04:48,020
有坏消息，美国来的

1304
02:04:48,480 --> 02:04:49,740
你哥哥桑尼

1305
02:04:50,930 --> 02:04:52,210
他们杀了他

1306
02:04:58,450 --> 02:05:02,630
我们走了  你答应的

1307
02:05:20,640 --> 02:05:22,190
- 法布里吉奥  - 什么事？
- Fabrizio. - Yes, sir?

1308
02:05:22,200 --> 02:05:24,100
备车

1309
02:05:24,110 --> 02:05:25,880
你要自己开吗，老板？
Are you driving yourself, boss?

1310
02:05:25,890 --> 02:05:26,970
是的
Yes.

1311
02:05:26,980 --> 02:05:28,490
你妻子跟你一起去吗？
Is your wife coming with you?

1312
02:05:28,500 --> 02:05:32,080
不，我要你送她回娘家，等一切安全点再说
Take her to her father's house till I know things are safe.

1313
02:05:32,090 --> 02:05:34,200
好的，随你吩咐，老板
Anything you say, boss.

1314
02:05:40,310 --> 02:05:42,420
卡罗  阿波罗妮娅呢？

1315
02:05:43,000 --> 02:05:47,110
她想给你个惊喜，她要开车

1316
02:05:48,770 --> 02:05:51,910
她会当个好的美国太太

1317
02:05:52,370 --> 02:05:54,650
等一下  我去拿行李

1318
02:06:04,590 --> 02:06:05,740
法布里吉奥

1319
02:06:07,020 --> 02:06:08,440
你要去哪里？

1320
02:06:09,590 --> 02:06:13,150
迈克尔，在那边等着，我开过去

1321
02:06:18,740 --> 02:06:21,110
不！不，阿波罗妮娅…

1322
02:06:43,450 --> 02:06:49,130
唐・巴茨尼，我要谢谢你帮我组织今天这次会议
Don Barzini, I want to thank you for helping me organize this meeting here today.

1323
02:06:49,500 --> 02:06:54,860
还有其它五大家族的首领，纽约和新泽西的
And also the other heads of the five families... from New York and New Jersey.

1324
02:06:56,060 --> 02:06:59,210
布朗克斯区的卡迈恩・柯尼奥
Carmine Cuneo from the Bronx.

1325
02:06:59,220 --> 02:07:03,020
以及…布鲁克林的
From Brooklyn...

1326
02:07:04,330 --> 02:07:06,490
菲利普・塔塔利亚
Philip Tattaglia.

1327
02:07:07,900 --> 02:07:10,350
来自斯塔顿岛的
And from Staten Island...

1328
02:07:10,850 --> 02:07:14,310
维克多・斯特拉基
we have with us Victor Strachi.

1329
02:07:14,340 --> 02:07:20,060
以及所有其他的伙伴们，远自加州和堪萨斯城
And all the other associates that came as far... as from California and Kansas City...

1330
02:07:20,070 --> 02:07:22,910
以及全国其它各地区
and all the other territories of the country.

1331
02:07:22,920 --> 02:07:24,810
谢谢你们
Thank you.

1332
02:07:30,780 --> 02:07:33,110
事情怎么会搞得这么过火？
How did things ever get so far?

1333
02:07:34,210 --> 02:07:35,630
我不知道
I don't know.

1334
02:07:37,990 --> 02:07:42,520
如此的不幸，如此没有必要
It was so unfortunate and so unnecessary.

1335
02:07:44,580 --> 02:07:46,650
塔塔利亚失去了一个儿子
Tattaglia lost a son...

1336
02:07:46,790 --> 02:07:48,070
我也失去了一个儿子
and I lost a son.

1337
02:07:50,340 --> 02:07:51,770
我们两抵了
We're quits

1338
02:07:51,780 --> 02:07:53,740
如果塔塔利亚同意
and if Tattaglia agrees...

1339
02:07:53,910 --> 02:07:58,430
我愿意 让事情回到过去的路子上
then I'm willing to let things go on the way they were before.

1340
02:07:59,440 --> 02:08:02,880
我们都感谢唐・柯利昂尼 召开这次会议
We are all grateful to Don Corleone for calling this meeting.

1341
02:08:03,040 --> 02:08:05,430
我们都了解他是个说话算数的人
We all know him as a man of his word.

1342
02:08:05,810 --> 02:08:08,470
一个谦虚的人，总是能听进去道理
A modest man. He'll always listen to reason.

1343
02:08:08,480 --> 02:08:10,340
是的，唐・巴茨尼
Yes, Don Barzini.

1344
02:08:10,670 --> 02:08:12,780
他太谦虚了
He's too modest.

1345
02:08:12,790 --> 02:08:16,810
他有那么多法官和政客在自己口袋里
He had all the judges and politicians in his pocket.

1346
02:08:16,980 --> 02:08:19,410
他却拒绝分享他们
He refused to share them.

1347
02:08:20,040 --> 02:08:23,770
何时？我何时拒绝过通融？
When？ When did I ever refuse an accommodation?

1348
02:08:23,830 --> 02:08:25,740
你们在座的全都认识我
All of you know me here.

1349
02:08:27,140 --> 02:08:31,010
我何时曾经拒绝过？除了一次
When did I ever refuse, except one time?

1350
02:08:31,430 --> 02:08:32,390
那为什么呢？
And why?

1351
02:08:34,030 --> 02:08:39,470
因为我相信毒品生意 在往后几年会毁了我们
Because I believe this drug business...is gonna destroy us in the years to come.

1352
02:08:39,850 --> 02:08:44,180
我是说，它不像赌博、酒类或甚至女人
I mean, it's not like gambling or liquor or even women...

1353
02:08:44,210 --> 02:08:46,600
那是如今多数人想要的东西
which is something that most people want nowadays

1354
02:08:46,610 --> 02:08:50,330
被教会的大人物[意大利语]所禁止
and is forbidden to them by the pezzonovante of the church.

1355
02:08:50,340 --> 02:08:55,080
即使警察过去在赌博和其它方面一直帮我们
Even the police departments that have helped us in the past with gambling and other things

1356
02:08:55,090 --> 02:08:58,710
但一提到毒品 他们会拒绝帮忙
are gonna refuse to help us when it comes to narcotics.

1357
02:08:59,430 --> 02:09:04,340
那时候我相信是这样，现在我也相信
And I believed that then... and I believe that now.

1358
02:09:04,590 --> 02:09:06,620
时代已经变了
Times have changed.

1359
02:09:06,850 --> 02:09:09,010
不像往日那样了
It's not like the old days...

1360
02:09:09,170 --> 02:09:11,410
那时我们能为所欲为
when we could do anything we want.

1361
02:09:11,740 --> 02:09:14,420
拒绝不是为友之道
A refusal is not the act of a friend.

1362
02:09:14,610 --> 02:09:18,730
如果唐・柯利昂尼掌握纽约全体法官和政客
If Don Corleone had all the judges and politicians in New York...

1363
02:09:18,740 --> 02:09:21,760
那他就必须分享，或让我们都能利用他们
then he must share them or let others use them.

1364
02:09:21,810 --> 02:09:25,110
他必须让我们从这口井里打水
He must let us draw the water from the well.

1365
02:09:25,850 --> 02:09:29,210
当然，他可以为这样的服务开出账单
Certainly, he can present a bill for such services.

1366
02:09:29,540 --> 02:09:32,710
毕竟，我们不是共产党
After all, we are not Communists.

1367
02:09:35,370 --> 02:09:37,870
我同样不相信毒品
I also don't believe in drugs.

1368
02:09:38,510 --> 02:09:40,810
多年来我额外付费给我的人
For years, I paid my people extra...

1369
02:09:40,830 --> 02:09:43,060
让他们不去做那种生意
so they wouldn't do that kind of business.

1370
02:09:43,480 --> 02:09:46,550
有人来找他们，并且说：“我有白粉
Somebody comes to them and says, "I have powders.

1371
02:09:46,560 --> 02:09:50,090
“只要你投入3、4千资金
If you put up a three, four-thousand-dollar investment...

1372
02:09:50,360 --> 02:09:53,520
“我们可以赚到5万来分”
we can make 50,000 distributing."

1373
02:09:54,110 --> 02:09:55,530
所以他们不能抵抗
So they can't resist.

1374
02:09:55,560 --> 02:10:00,260
我想要把它作为一门生意控制好，保持正派
I want to control it as a business...to keep it respectable.

1375
02:10:00,470 --> 02:10:02,340
我不要它接近学校
I don't want it near schools.

1376
02:10:02,350 --> 02:10:04,670
我不要把它卖给孩子
I don't want it sold to children.

1377
02:10:05,180 --> 02:10:07,500
那是丧良心的[意大利语]
That's an infamia.

1378
02:10:08,340 --> 02:10:12,240
在我的城市，我们会把买卖保持在黑人，有色人种当中
In my city, we'll keep the traffic in the dark people, the colored.

1379
02:10:12,250 --> 02:10:16,060
他们反正是动物，所以让他们灵魂堕落吧
They're animals anyway, so let them lose their souls.

1380
02:10:22,110 --> 02:10:26,170
我早希望我们能到这里来，一起讲讲道理
I hoped that we could come here and reason together.

1381
02:10:27,110 --> 02:10:30,940
身为一个讲道理的人，我愿意做任何事…
As a reasonable man, I'm willing to do whatever's necessary to...

1382
02:10:31,290 --> 02:10:34,180
为这些问题找到一个和平的解决方案
find a peaceful solution to these problems.

1383
02:10:34,230 --> 02:10:35,610
那我们就都同意了
Then we are agreed.

1384
02:10:36,020 --> 02:10:38,790
毒品买卖将会获准，但要有控制
The traffic in drugs will be permitted but controlled.

1385
02:10:38,810 --> 02:10:41,880
唐・柯利昂尼会给我们东部的保护
Don Corleone will give us protection in the east...

1386
02:10:41,890 --> 02:10:43,540
这样就有和平
and there will be the peace.

1387
02:10:43,550 --> 02:10:46,410
但我必须有唐・柯利昂尼的直接担保
But I must have strict assurance from Corleone.

1388
02:10:47,140 --> 02:10:50,510
随着时间推移，他的地位变得更强大…
As time goes by and his position becomes stronger...

1389
02:10:50,530 --> 02:10:53,070
他会不会意图报血仇？
will he attempt any individual vendetta?

1390
02:10:53,080 --> 02:10:55,160
你看，我们这全是讲理的人
Look, we are all reasonable men here.

1391
02:10:55,170 --> 02:10:58,310
我们不必给出保证，好像我们是律师
We don't have to give assurances as if we were lawyers.

1392
02:10:58,660 --> 02:11:00,220
你说到复仇
You talk about vengeance.

1393
02:11:01,440 --> 02:11:04,130
复仇会把你儿子带回给你吗？
Is vengeance gonna bring your son back to you?

1394
02:11:04,720 --> 02:11:07,060
或把我的儿子给我？
Or my boy to me?

1395
02:11:07,260 --> 02:11:10,520
我放弃为我儿子复仇
I forego the vengeance of my son.

1396
02:11:13,020 --> 02:11:15,630
但我有自私的理由
But I have selfish reasons.

1397
02:11:17,620 --> 02:11:21,980
我最小的儿子，被迫离开这个国家
My youngest son...was forced to leave this country...

1398
02:11:23,130 --> 02:11:25,090
因为索洛佐这件事
because of this Sollozzo business.

1399
02:11:26,070 --> 02:11:30,890
好吧，我必须做出各种安排，把他安全带回来
All right. And I have to make arrangements to bring him back here safely.

1400
02:11:31,110 --> 02:11:34,140
澄清所有这些错误的指控
cleared of all these false charges.

1401
02:11:35,290 --> 02:11:37,740
但我是个迷信的人
But I'm a superstitious man.

1402
02:11:38,440 --> 02:11:40,850
如果有什么不幸意外落在他身上
And if some unlucky accident should befall him--

1403
02:11:40,860 --> 02:11:44,690
如果他被一个警官开枪打中脑袋
if he should get shot in the head by a police officer...

1404
02:11:45,130 --> 02:11:48,820
或如果他在自己的牢房里上吊
or if he should hang himself in his jail cell...

1405
02:11:48,860 --> 02:11:52,280
或如果他被一道闪电击中
of if he's struck by a bolt of lightening--

1406
02:11:52,960 --> 02:11:56,410
那我将怪罪这房间里的某些人
then I'm going to blame some of the people in this room.

1407
02:11:58,270 --> 02:12:00,710
那是我不会原谅的
And that I do not forgive.

1408
02:12:03,090 --> 02:12:06,050
但是，除此之外…
But that aside...

1409
02:12:08,520 --> 02:12:15,250
我可以说我发誓，以我孙子的灵魂
let me say that I swear... on the souls of my grandchildren...

1410
02:12:15,730 --> 02:12:20,100
我不会是打破我们今天和议的人
that I will not be the one to break the peace we've made here today.

1411
02:12:45,530 --> 02:12:47,410
我跟见塔塔利亚的人会面时…
When I meet with the Tattaglia people...

1412
02:12:47,420 --> 02:12:50,710
要不要坚持那些毒品中间人 都没有前科？
should I insist that all these drug middlemen have clean records?

1413
02:12:51,120 --> 02:12:53,620
提出来即可，不要坚持
Mention it. Don't insist.

1414
02:12:55,360 --> 02:12:58,480
巴茨尼是个不用说也明白的人
Barzini is a man who'll know that without being told.

1415
02:12:59,170 --> 02:13:00,530
你是说塔塔利亚
You mean Tattaglia.

1416
02:13:02,070 --> 02:13:03,380
塔塔利亚是个拉皮条的
Tattaglia's a pimp.

1417
02:13:04,740 --> 02:13:08,060
他根本不可能干掉桑提诺
He never could've outfought Santino.

1418
02:13:10,550 --> 02:13:13,640
但我直到今天以前并不知道，这事……
But I didn't know until this day that it was...

1419
02:13:14,480 --> 02:13:16,550
一直是巴茨尼做的
Barzini all along.

1420
02:13:31,510 --> 02:13:32,960
来吧，南希
Come on, Nancy.

1421
02:13:34,760 --> 02:13:37,940
大家待在一起  布莱恩
Keep together, everyone. Brian?

1422
02:13:38,740 --> 02:13:40,770
好了，对了
Okay. All right.

1423
02:13:53,760 --> 02:13:55,360
你回来多久了？
How long have you been back?

1424
02:13:56,510 --> 02:13:57,810
我回来一年了
I've been back a year.

1425
02:13:59,700 --> 02:14:01,680
我觉得还要长
Longer than that, I think.

1426
02:14:04,520 --> 02:14:06,720
见到你真好，凯伊
It's good to see you, Kay.

1427
02:14:17,740 --> 02:14:20,220
我现在为我父亲做事，凯伊
I'm working for my father now, Kay.

1428
02:14:22,820 --> 02:14:26,120
他一直病着，病得很重
He's been sick.Very sick.

1429
02:14:27,390 --> 02:14:29,310
可你并不像他，迈克尔
But you're not like him, Michael.

1430
02:14:29,410 --> 02:14:32,170
我以为你不会变成你父亲那样的人
I thought you weren't going to become a man like your father.

1431
02:14:32,180 --> 02:14:33,720
那是你告诉我的
That's what you told me.

1432
02:14:35,070 --> 02:14:38,110
我父亲跟其他有权的人没有区别
My father's no different than any other powerful man.

1433
02:14:39,530 --> 02:14:43,870
那种对其他人负有责任的人
Any man who's responsible for other people.

1434
02:14:44,140 --> 02:14:46,310
像是参议员或总统
Like a senator or a president.

1435
02:14:46,730 --> 02:14:48,570
你知道你说得多天真吗？
Do you know how naive you sound?

1436
02:14:48,580 --> 02:14:49,260
为什么？
Why?

1437
02:14:49,270 --> 02:14:52,410
参议员和总统不会派人杀人
Senators and presidents don't have men killed.

1438
02:14:55,120 --> 02:14:57,110
是谁天真，凯伊？
Who's being naive, Kay?

1439
02:14:58,430 --> 02:15:01,450
凯伊，我父亲做事的方法已经过时，结束了
Kay, my father's way of doing things is over. It's finished.

1440
02:15:01,810 --> 02:15:03,650
他也知道这一点
Even he knows that.

1441
02:15:04,160 --> 02:15:08,810
我是说 在五年柯利昂尼家族会完全合法化
I mean, in five years the Corleone family is going to be completely legitimate.

1442
02:15:10,370 --> 02:15:13,310
相信我，有关我的公事，我只能告诉你这些
Trust me. That's all I can tell you about my business.

1443
02:15:13,520 --> 02:15:14,510
凯伊
Kay

1444
02:15:15,810 --> 02:15:17,590
迈克尔，你为什么要来这里？
Michael, why did you come here?

1445
02:15:18,070 --> 02:15:19,540
为什么？
Why?

1446
02:15:20,460 --> 02:15:25,180
你想要我怎样？这么长时间连电话也没有，也没有信
What do you want with me after all this time without even calling or writing?

1447
02:15:25,310 --> 02:15:27,120
我来是因为我需要你
I came here because I need you.

1448
02:15:27,310 --> 02:15:28,720
因为我关心你
Because I care for you.

1449
02:15:28,730 --> 02:15:30,940
- 请别说了，迈克尔  - 因为…
- Please stop it, Michael. -Because...

1450
02:15:31,450 --> 02:15:32,920
我想要你嫁给我
I want you to marry me.

1451
02:15:34,410 --> 02:15:37,440
- 太迟了，太迟了…  - 求你，凯伊
- It's too late. - Please, Kay.

1452
02:15:38,620 --> 02:15:41,360
你要我做什么我都愿意，任何事，来弥补…
I'll do anything you ask, anything to make up

1453
02:15:41,420 --> 02:15:43,390
我俩过去发生的事
for what's happened to us.

1454
02:15:44,580 --> 02:15:46,810
因为那很重要，凯伊
Because that's important, Kay.

1455
02:15:46,820 --> 02:15:49,590
因为重要的是…
Because what's important is that...

1456
02:15:50,270 --> 02:15:51,510
我们拥有彼此
we have each other.

1457
02:15:52,070 --> 02:15:54,370
是我们要共度一生
That we have a life together.

1458
02:15:55,170 --> 02:15:56,720
是我们要有孩子
That we have children--

1459
02:15:56,740 --> 02:15:57,850
我们的孩子
our children.

1460
02:15:59,370 --> 02:16:00,310
凯伊
Kay.

1461
02:16:00,720 --> 02:16:01,910
我需要你
I need you...

1462
02:16:03,380 --> 02:16:05,620
而且我爱你
and I love you.

1463
02:16:27,260 --> 02:16:29,360
巴茨尼的人楔进我的地盘
Barzini's people chisel my territory...

1464
02:16:29,370 --> 02:16:31,110
而我们却什么也没做
and we do nothing about it.

1465
02:16:31,120 --> 02:16:33,920
很快我在布鲁克林就连挂帽子的地方都没有了
Pretty soon, there won't be one place in Brooklyn I can hang my hat.

1466
02:16:33,930 --> 02:16:34,850
耐心点
Just be patient.

1467
02:16:34,860 --> 02:16:38,020
我不是求你帮忙，麦克，只是不想受掣肘
I'm not askin' you for help, Mike. I just take off the handcuffs.

1468
02:16:38,040 --> 02:16:39,310
耐心点
Be patient.

1469
02:16:39,320 --> 02:16:41,220
我们必须保护自己
We gotta protect ourselves.

1470
02:16:41,230 --> 02:16:43,220
给我个机会招募一些新人
Give me a chance to recruit some new men.

1471
02:16:43,230 --> 02:16:44,330
不
No.

1472
02:16:44,920 --> 02:16:47,530
我不想给巴茨尼借口来开战
I don't wanna give Barzini an excuse to start fighting.

1473
02:16:47,540 --> 02:16:48,850
麦克，你错了
Mike, you're wrong.

1474
02:16:50,210 --> 02:16:51,310
唐・柯利昂尼
Don Corleone,

1475
02:16:52,470 --> 02:16:56,580
你曾说过 要让我跟泰西欧有一天能自立门户
you once said the day would come when Tessio and me could form our own family.

1476
02:16:56,590 --> 02:16:58,580
今天以前 我绝对没想过
Till today, I would never think of it.

1477
02:16:58,590 --> 02:17:00,690
我要求你的批准
I must ask your permission.

1478
02:17:01,540 --> 02:17:04,420
现在迈克尔是家族首领
Well, Michael is now head of the family and

1479
02:17:04,430 --> 02:17:07,820
如果他准许了，我就祝福你
if he gives his permission, then you have my blessing.

1480
02:17:08,870 --> 02:17:11,120
等我们搬到内华达州后
After we make the move to Nevada...

1481
02:17:11,170 --> 02:17:13,880
你就可以从柯利昂尼家族分出去，自立门户
you can break off from the Corleone family and go on your own.

1482
02:17:14,350 --> 02:17:15,660
等我们搬到内华达州之后
After we make the move to Nevada.

1483
02:17:15,670 --> 02:17:17,160
那会有多久？
How long will that be?

1484
02:17:18,780 --> 02:17:20,330
6个月
Six months.

1485
02:17:20,340 --> 02:17:23,230
原谅我，教父，但你这一走…
Forgive me, Godfather, but with you gone...

1486
02:17:23,540 --> 02:17:26,620
我跟彼得迟早会被巴茨尼捏在手中
me and Pete'll come under Barzini's thumb sooner or later.

1487
02:17:26,630 --> 02:17:28,480
我恨那该死的巴茨尼
And I hate that goddamn Barzini.

1488
02:17:28,490 --> 02:17:31,860
6个月的时间，剩不下什么给我们建设了
In six months' time, there won't be nothing left to build on.

1489
02:17:32,130 --> 02:17:34,480
你们对我的判断有信心吗？
You have faith in my judgment?

1490
02:17:34,630 --> 02:17:36,520
- 是的  - 你们对我忠心吗？
- Yes.  - Do I have your loyalty?

1491
02:17:36,640 --> 02:17:38,240
是的，一向如此，教父
Yes, always, Godfather.

1492
02:17:38,250 --> 02:17:40,120
那就当迈克尔的朋友吧
Then be a friend to Michael...

1493
02:17:40,380 --> 02:17:42,410
照他说的做
and do as he says.

1494
02:17:46,320 --> 02:17:48,060
现在有些事仍在磋商…
There are things being negotiated now...

1495
02:17:48,070 --> 02:17:51,620
将会解决你们的所有问题，解答所有疑问
that are gonna solve all your problems and answer all your questions.

1496
02:17:51,790 --> 02:17:53,760
现在我只能告诉你们这些
That's all I can tell you now.

1497
02:17:55,010 --> 02:17:57,130
卡洛，你在内华达长大
Carlo, you grew up in Nevada.

1498
02:17:57,540 --> 02:18:00,640
等我们搬过去的时候，你会是我的左右手
When we make our move there, you're gonna be my right-hand man.

1499
02:18:01,010 --> 02:18:03,310
汤姆・黑根不再做Consigliere了
Tom Hagen's no longer consigliere.

1500
02:18:03,570 --> 02:18:05,660
他将会是我们在维加斯的律师
He's gonna be our lawyer in Vegas.

1501
02:18:06,010 --> 02:18:08,520
对汤姆没有不满，但我想要这样
That's no reflection on Tom, but that's the way I want it.

1502
02:18:08,580 --> 02:18:12,740
再说，要是我需要什么建议，有比我父亲更好的Consigliere吗？Consigliere
Besides, if I ever need help who's a better consigliere than my father?

1503
02:18:12,770 --> 02:18:13,830
就这些
That's it.

1504
02:18:27,110 --> 02:18:27,920
好的
All right.

1505
02:18:33,360 --> 02:18:36,020
- 谢谢，爸爸  - 我为你高兴，卡洛
- Thank you, Papa. - I'm happy for you, Carlo.

1506
02:18:37,470 --> 02:18:40,790
迈克尔…我为何出局了？
Michael...Why am I out?

1507
02:18:41,640 --> 02:18:44,660
你不适合当战时Consigliere
You're not a wartime consigliere.

1508
02:18:45,720 --> 02:18:48,940
随着我们这次转移，情况会变得棘手
Things may get rough with the move we're trying.

1509
02:18:49,050 --> 02:18:50,430
汤姆
Tom.

1510
02:18:55,430 --> 02:18:57,440
我跟迈克尔建议的
I advised Michael.

1511
02:18:57,590 --> 02:19:00,630
我从不认为你是个糟糕的Consigliere
I never thought you were a bad consigliere.

1512
02:19:00,740 --> 02:19:04,010
我认为…桑提诺是个糟糕的唐
I thought Santino was a bad Don...

1513
02:19:04,020 --> 02:19:06,020
愿他安息
rest in peace.

1514
02:19:06,280 --> 02:19:10,090
我对迈克尔完全信任，对你也是
Michael has all my confidence, as you do.

1515
02:19:10,530 --> 02:19:11,700
但是…
But...

1516
02:19:11,910 --> 02:19:16,210
要你不参与即将发生的事情 是有理由的
there are reasons why you must have no part of what is going to happen.

1517
02:19:16,520 --> 02:19:18,050
也许我能帮上忙
Maybe I could help.

1518
02:19:18,210 --> 02:19:20,020
你出局了，汤姆
You're out, Tom.

1519
02:20:08,930 --> 02:20:11,550
我无法不注意你脸的模样
I can't get over the way your face looks.

1520
02:20:11,570 --> 02:20:13,220
它看起来真的很棒
It really looks good.

1521
02:20:13,240 --> 02:20:14,880
这医生干得不错
This doctor did some job.

1522
02:20:14,920 --> 02:20:16,210
谁说服你去的，凯伊吗？
Who talked you into it, Kay?

1523
02:20:16,220 --> 02:20:18,640
喂喂喂，把它们留在这里
Hey, hey, wait. Leave them out here.

1524
02:20:18,650 --> 02:20:20,020
我们待会儿再处理它们
We'll deal with them later.

1525
02:20:20,030 --> 02:20:21,440
他累了，他要梳洗一下
He's tired. He wants to clean up.

1526
02:20:21,450 --> 02:20:23,650
好了，现在我来开门好吗？
All right, now, let me open the door, all right?

1527
02:20:30,640 --> 02:20:32,820
你好，麦克，欢迎光临拉斯维加斯
Hello, Mike. Welcome to Las Vegas.

1528
02:20:32,830 --> 02:20:34,190
全是为你准备的，小子
All for you, kid.

1529
02:20:34,210 --> 02:20:36,180
都是他的主意  对吧？
It was all his idea, right?

1530
02:20:36,190 --> 02:20:37,170
哦，你哥哥弗雷多…
Well, your brother, Freddy--

1531
02:20:37,180 --> 02:20:39,340
- 都是约翰尼…  - 女孩们来…
- It was Johnny--  - Girls here?

1532
02:20:42,760 --> 02:20:45,910
- 我就回来，你让她们别闲着  - 好，好的
- I'll be right back. You keep them occupied. - All right. Okay.

1533
02:20:45,920 --> 02:20:46,760
这才对
That a boy, huh?

1534
02:20:46,960 --> 02:20:48,760
你要什么都有，小子，都有
Anything you want, kid, anything.

1535
02:20:49,080 --> 02:20:50,160
那些女孩子是谁？
Who are the girls?

1536
02:20:51,890 --> 02:20:53,810
这得要你来搞清楚了
That's for you to find out.

1537
02:20:53,830 --> 02:20:55,620
把她们弄走，弗雷多
Get rid of them, Fredo

1538
02:20:56,680 --> 02:20:57,800
喂，麦克
Hey, Mike--

1539
02:20:57,810 --> 02:20:59,740
弗雷多，我是来办公事的，明天就走
Fredo, I'm here on business. I leave tomorrow.

1540
02:20:59,750 --> 02:21:00,940
现在把她们弄走
Now, get rid of them.

1541
02:21:01,780 --> 02:21:04,950
我累了  把乐队也弄走
I'm tired. Get rid of the band too.

1542
02:21:10,270 --> 02:21:13,530
喂，走吧，来吧，走人，走吧
Hey, just take off. Come on, take off. Let's go, come on.

1543
02:21:13,540 --> 02:21:16,310
喂，结束了，安杰洛，结束了
Hey, that's it. Angelo, that's it.

1544
02:21:16,340 --> 02:21:17,350
来，走吧
Come on, let's go.

1545
02:21:17,440 --> 02:21:19,410
喂，快点，赶紧走！
Hey, come on! Scram!

1546
02:21:21,170 --> 02:21:22,240
走吧，亲，走了
Scram! Come on, honey. Let's go.

1547
02:21:22,250 --> 02:21:23,520
我不知道  约翰尼
I don't know, Johnny.

1548
02:21:23,650 --> 02:21:25,820
我不知道他是怎么回事，对不起
I don't know what the hell's the matter with him, I'm sorry.

1549
02:21:25,830 --> 02:21:27,690
没关系，没事的，弗雷迪
It's all right. It's all right, Freddy.

1550
02:21:28,070 --> 02:21:30,730
我不知道，他大概累了
I don't know. He's tired, he's hot.

1551
02:21:37,660 --> 02:21:39,540
莫・格林怎么回事？
What happened to Moe Greene?

1552
02:21:40,680 --> 02:21:41,950
他说他有别的事
He said he had some business.

1553
02:21:41,960 --> 02:21:45,170
他说等派对开始时  给他打个电话
He said give him a call...when the party started.

1554
02:21:45,240 --> 02:21:46,850
那就给他打个电话
Well, give him a call.

1555
02:21:48,350 --> 02:21:49,760
约翰尼，你好吗？
Johnny, how are you?

1556
02:21:49,810 --> 02:21:51,630
你好，迈克尔，真高兴再见到你
Hello, Michael, nice to see you again.

1557
02:21:51,640 --> 02:21:52,850
我们全都以你为傲
We're all proud of you.

1558
02:21:52,950 --> 02:21:54,060
谢谢，迈克尔
Thanks, Mike.

1559
02:21:54,080 --> 02:21:55,740
坐下，约翰尼，我要跟你谈谈
Sit down,Johnny. I want to talk to you.

1560
02:21:56,230 --> 02:21:57,660
唐也以你为傲，约翰尼
The Don's proud of you too, Johnny.

1561
02:21:57,670 --> 02:22:00,550
我的一切都是欠他的
Well, I owe it all to him.

1562
02:22:00,830 --> 02:22:02,820
他知道你有多感恩
Well, he knows how grateful you are.

1563
02:22:02,830 --> 02:22:05,980
所以…他想请你帮个忙
That's why he'd like to ask a favor of you.

1564
02:22:06,090 --> 02:22:07,710
麦克，我能做些什么？
Mike, what can I do?

1565
02:22:09,280 --> 02:22:13,310
柯利昂尼家族在考虑放弃橄榄油生意上的全部投资
The Corleone family is thinking of giving up all its interests in the olive oil business

1566
02:22:13,330 --> 02:22:14,610
在这里安顿下来
settling out here.

1567
02:22:15,430 --> 02:22:18,940
莫・格林会卖给我们 他在赌场及酒店的所有股份
Now, Moe Greene will sell us his share of the casino and hotel...

1568
02:22:18,950 --> 02:22:20,870
这样它能完全为家族所有
so it can be completely owned by the family.

1569
02:22:21,010 --> 02:22:23,750
- 汤姆  - 麦克，这你确定吗？
- Tom.  - Mike, are you sure about that?

1570
02:22:23,790 --> 02:22:24,940
莫热爱这门生意
Moe loves the business.

1571
02:22:24,950 --> 02:22:26,870
他从未对我提过要卖掉它的事
He never said nothin' to me about sellin'.

1572
02:22:26,880 --> 02:22:29,510
我会提个他无法拒绝的条件
I'll make him an offer he can't refuse.

1573
02:22:30,910 --> 02:22:32,500
你看，约翰尼…
See,Johnny...

1574
02:22:33,370 --> 02:22:35,810
你看，我们估计娱乐表演会是很强的因素
See, we figure that entertainment will be a big factor

1575
02:22:35,820 --> 02:22:37,680
把赌客拉进到赌场来
in drawing gamblers to the casino.

1576
02:22:37,720 --> 02:22:41,400
我们希望你签个合约 一年登台五次
We hope you'll sign a contract to appear five times a year.

1577
02:22:44,340 --> 02:22:49,310
也许还能…劝说一些你在电影圈的朋友，也这么做
Perhaps convince some of your friends in the movies to do the same.

1578
02:22:50,260 --> 02:22:51,930
我指望你了
We're counting on you.

1579
02:22:54,380 --> 02:22:55,310
当然，麦克
Sure, Mike.

1580
02:22:55,620 --> 02:22:57,910
为我的教父我什么都肯做，这你知道
I'll do anything for my godfather. You know that.

1581
02:22:58,380 --> 02:22:59,210
好
Good.

1582
02:23:01,170 --> 02:23:03,770
嘿，麦克，各位好，大家都在这里
Hey, Mike. Hello, fellas. Everybody's here.

1583
02:23:03,780 --> 02:23:05,640
弗雷迪，汤姆…
Freddy, Tom.

1584
02:23:05,910 --> 02:23:07,870
- 见到你真好，麦克  - 你好吗，莫？
Good to see you, Mike. How are you, Moe?

1585
02:23:07,880 --> 02:23:09,210
好，你要的都齐了吗？
All right. You got everything you want?

1586
02:23:09,220 --> 02:23:10,440
厨师给你做特餐
The chef cooked for you special,

1587
02:23:10,450 --> 02:23:13,450
舞蹈能让你咋舌，你的信用蛮好的
the dancers will kick your tongue out and your credit is good.

1588
02:23:13,460 --> 02:23:16,660
弄点筹码给房间里每个人，让他们到场子里去玩玩
Draw chips for everybody in the room so they can play on the house.

1589
02:23:19,880 --> 02:23:22,290
我的信用好到够买下你吗？
My credit good enough to buy you out?

1590
02:23:24,170 --> 02:23:25,710
买下我？
Buy me out?

1591
02:23:26,310 --> 02:23:28,550
这个赌场，这家酒店
The casino. The hotel.

1592
02:23:28,990 --> 02:23:31,680
柯利昂尼家族想买下你全部的生意
The Corleone family wants to buy you out.

1593
02:23:31,920 --> 02:23:34,650
柯利昂尼家族想买下我？
The Corleone family wants to buy me out?

1594
02:23:34,870 --> 02:23:37,310
不，我买下你们，你们买不下我
No, I buy you out. You don't buy me out.

1595
02:23:37,360 --> 02:23:39,230
你的赌场赔钱了
Your casino loses money.

1596
02:23:39,240 --> 02:23:40,820
也许我们能做得更好些
Maybe we can do better.

1597
02:23:40,830 --> 02:23:42,820
你以为我滑下顶峰了，迈克尔？
You think I'm skimming off the top, Mike?

1598
02:23:44,110 --> 02:23:45,360
你运气不好
You're unlucky.

1599
02:23:49,670 --> 02:23:52,220
你这该死的意大利佬真把我逗乐了
You goddamn guineas really make me laugh.

1600
02:23:52,230 --> 02:23:55,210
你们有难时 我帮你们忙收留弗雷迪
I do you a favor and take Freddy in when you're having a bad time.

1601
02:23:55,220 --> 02:23:56,430
现在你想把我挤走
Then you try to push me out!

1602
02:23:56,450 --> 02:23:57,620
等一下
Wait a minute.

1603
02:23:58,030 --> 02:24:01,420
你收留弗雷迪，是因为柯利昂尼家族给你的赌场财政支援
You took Freddy in because the Corleone family bankrolled your casino...

1604
02:24:01,430 --> 02:24:03,630
因为海岸的莫伦纳里家族
because the Molinari family on the coast...

1605
02:24:03,640 --> 02:24:05,030
保证他的安全
guaranteed his safety.

1606
02:24:05,040 --> 02:24:07,030
现在我们谈的是生意，我们来谈谈生意
Now, we're talkin' business. Let's talk business.

1607
02:24:07,040 --> 02:24:08,210
好，我们来谈生意，麦克
Let's talk business, Mike.

1608
02:24:08,540 --> 02:24:09,930
首先，你们都完了
First of all, you're all done.

1609
02:24:09,940 --> 02:24:12,310
柯利昂尼家族再也没有那么强大了
The Corleone family don't even have that kind of muscle anymore.

1610
02:24:12,320 --> 02:24:13,740
教父生病了，对吧？
The Godfather's sick, right?

1611
02:24:13,790 --> 02:24:16,660
你们被巴茨尼及其它家族 赶出了纽约
You're getting chased out of New York...by Barzini and the other families.

1612
02:24:16,820 --> 02:24:17,990
你以为是怎么回事？
What do you think is gonna on?

1613
02:24:18,010 --> 02:24:20,440
你以为能到我的酒店来接管？
You think you can come to my hotel and take over?

1614
02:24:20,940 --> 02:24:22,550
我和巴茨尼谈过
I talked to Barzini.

1615
02:24:22,560 --> 02:24:25,540
我可以跟他做一笔交易，而且仍然保留我的酒店
I can make a deal with him and still keep my hotel.

1616
02:24:26,010 --> 02:24:28,010
所以你就当众掌掴我哥哥吗？
Is that why you slapped my brother around in public?

1617
02:24:29,580 --> 02:24:31,680
哦，不，那不算什么，麦克
Oh, no, that was nothin', Mike.

1618
02:24:31,690 --> 02:24:34,420
那个…莫那样做没别的意思
Now, now...Moe didn't mean nothin' by that.

1619
02:24:34,430 --> 02:24:36,810
当然他时不时会发火，但是…
Sure he flies off the handle once in a while, but...

1620
02:24:36,880 --> 02:24:38,820
但莫和我是好朋友，对吧，莫？
but Moe and me, we're good friends, right, Moe?

1621
02:24:38,850 --> 02:24:40,450
我要经营生意
I got a business to run.

1622
02:24:40,860 --> 02:24:43,650
我有时候得严厉些，是为了好好经营
I gotta kick asses sometimes to make it run right.

1623
02:24:43,660 --> 02:24:45,260
我们有点小争执，弗雷迪跟我
We had a little argument, Freddy and I

1624
02:24:45,270 --> 02:24:47,310
所以我不得不纠正他
so I had to straighten him out.

1625
02:24:47,690 --> 02:24:49,740
你纠正我哥哥？
You straightened my brother out?

1626
02:24:50,550 --> 02:24:53,110
他一次搞两个鸡尾酒女郎
He was banging cocktail waitresses two at a time!

1627
02:24:53,210 --> 02:24:55,110
赌客在桌上要不到酒
Players couldn't get a drink on the table.

1628
02:24:55,120 --> 02:24:56,310
你有什么毛病？
What's wrong with you?

1629
02:25:01,820 --> 02:25:03,610
我明天动身去纽约
I leave for New York tomorrow.

1630
02:25:04,110 --> 02:25:05,810
考虑一个价钱吧
Think about a price.

1631
02:25:06,070 --> 02:25:07,140
婊子养的
Son of a bitch.

1632
02:25:07,670 --> 02:25:10,340
你知道我是谁吗？我是莫・格林
Do you know who I am? I'm Moe Greene.

1633
02:25:10,370 --> 02:25:13,010
我进家族时你还在跟啦啦队长约会
I made my bones when you were going out with cheerleaders.

1634
02:25:13,030 --> 02:25:15,310
等等，莫，我有个主意
Wait a minute, Moe. Moe, I got an idea.

1635
02:25:16,560 --> 02:25:17,440
汤姆
Tom

1636
02:25:17,520 --> 02:25:18,740
汤姆，你是Consigliere
Tom, you're the consigliere.

1637
02:25:18,750 --> 02:25:21,310
- 你可以跟唐说说，你可以解释…  - 等一下
-You can talk to the Don. You can explain...-Just a minute.

1638
02:25:21,810 --> 02:25:25,470
唐已经半退休了，麦克现在负责家族事务
The Don is semiretired. Mike is in charge of the business now.

1639
02:25:25,470 --> 02:25:28,780
你有什么话说，跟迈克尔说吧
If you have anything to say, say it to Michael.

1640
02:25:32,750 --> 02:25:35,050
麦克，你不能到拉斯维加斯来
Mike! You don't come to Las Vegas

1641
02:25:35,060 --> 02:25:37,930
跟莫・格林那种人那样说话
and talk to a man like Moe Greene like that!

1642
02:25:39,440 --> 02:25:40,530
弗雷多
Fredo

1643
02:25:41,810 --> 02:25:44,530
你是我哥哥，而且我爱你
You're my older brother, and I love you.

1644
02:25:46,260 --> 02:25:50,360
但是再也别站在外人一边 反对家族了
But don't ever take sides with anyone...against the family again...

1645
02:25:51,630 --> 02:25:52,430
永远
ever.

1646
02:26:00,720 --> 02:26:02,650
我得先去看我父亲和他的手下
I have to see my father and his people.

1647
02:26:02,660 --> 02:26:03,960
所以别等我吃晚饭了
So have dinner without me.

1648
02:26:03,980 --> 02:26:05,530
迈克尔
Oh, Michael.

1649
02:26:06,910 --> 02:26:07,490
这个周末我们出去
This weekend we'll go out.

1650
02:26:07,600 --> 02:26:11,840
我们到城里去，看电影吃饭，我保证
We'll go to the city. We'll see a show and have dinner. I promise.

1651
02:26:19,070 --> 02:26:19,970
迈克尔
Michael.

1652
02:26:20,120 --> 02:26:22,110
迈克尔，你妹妹有事想问你
Michael, your sister wants to ask you something.

1653
02:26:22,130 --> 02:26:23,910
- 让她来问  - 不，她害怕
- Let her ask. - No, she's afraid to.

1654
02:26:24,120 --> 02:26:27,310
康妮和卡洛 想要你当他们孩子的教父
Connie and Carlo want you to be godfather to their little boy.

1655
02:26:27,360 --> 02:26:29,280
- 看情况吧  - 你会当吗？
- We'll see. - Will you?

1656
02:26:29,290 --> 02:26:31,310
让我考虑一下，看情况吧，来吧
Let me think about it. We'll see. Come on.

1657
02:26:38,380 --> 02:26:39,620
所以…
So...

1658
02:26:40,410 --> 02:26:42,960
巴茨尼会先一步对付你
Barzini will move against you first.

1659
02:26:43,420 --> 02:26:47,210
他会与一个你完全信任的人设计一次会面
He'll set up a meeting with someone that you absolutely trust...

1660
02:26:47,970 --> 02:26:50,370
保证你的安全
guaranteeing your safety.

1661
02:26:51,130 --> 02:26:54,630
然后在会面时，你会被暗杀
And at that meeting, you'll be assassinated.

1662
02:26:59,160 --> 02:27:01,410
我越来越比以前爱喝了
I like to drink wine more than I used to.

1663
02:27:03,530 --> 02:27:05,520
总之，我喝得更多了
Anyway, I'm drinking more.

1664
02:27:05,710 --> 02:27:07,440
对你有好处，爸爸
It's good for you, Pop.

1665
02:27:12,070 --> 02:27:13,910
我不知道
I don't know.

1666
02:27:15,580 --> 02:27:18,380
你妻子和孩子，你跟他们快乐吧？
Your wife and children, are you happy with them?

1667
02:27:19,390 --> 02:27:21,020
非常快乐
Very happy.

1668
02:27:21,430 --> 02:27:22,760
那就好
That's good.

1669
02:27:24,090 --> 02:27:29,060
希望你不介意 我一直在谈巴茨尼的事
I hope you don't mind the way I... I keep going over this Barzini business.

1670
02:27:29,130 --> 02:27:30,980
不，一点也不
No, not at all.

1671
02:27:31,120 --> 02:27:32,630
这是个老习惯
It's an old habit.

1672
02:27:33,510 --> 02:27:36,780
我一辈子努力不要粗心
I spent my life tryin' not to be careless.

1673
02:27:38,190 --> 02:27:41,470
女人和小孩能够粗心大意，但男人不行
Women and children can be careless, but not men.

1674
02:27:44,830 --> 02:27:47,340
- 你儿子怎么样？  - 他很好
- How's your boy? - He's good.

1675
02:27:47,360 --> 02:27:50,150
你知道他的样子一天天更像你了
You know, he looks more like you every day.

1676
02:27:52,860 --> 02:27:54,840
他比我聪明
He's smarter than I am.

1677
02:27:55,300 --> 02:27:57,830
三岁就能看漫画了
Three years old, he can read the funny papers.

1678
02:27:59,370 --> 02:28:01,660
他会看漫画
He reads the funny papers.

1679
02:28:08,610 --> 02:28:11,050
我要你安排一个电话公司的人
I want you to arrange to have a telephone man...

1680
02:28:11,060 --> 02:28:14,520
检查每一个进出这里的电话
check all the calls that go in and out of here.

1681
02:28:14,530 --> 02:28:17,820
- 我已经做了，爸  - 可能是任何人  - 爸，我已经处理了
- I did it already. - Could be anyone. - Pa, I took care of that.

1682
02:28:17,910 --> 02:28:20,450
哦，对，我忘了
Oh, that's right. I forgot.

1683
02:28:23,770 --> 02:28:25,390
怎么回事？
What's the matter?

1684
02:28:26,420 --> 02:28:28,260
是什么困扰着你？
What's bothering you?

1685
02:28:31,800 --> 02:28:33,030
我会应付的
I'll handle it.

1686
02:28:34,270 --> 02:28:37,230
我跟你说过我能应付，我会的应付的
I told you I can handle it, I'll handle it.

1687
02:28:49,760 --> 02:28:53,960
我知道桑提诺一定会经历这一切…
I knew that Santino was gonna have to go through all this...

1688
02:28:54,330 --> 02:28:56,440
还有弗雷多
and Fredo--

1689
02:28:58,690 --> 02:29:00,820
弗雷多他…
Fredo was--

1690
02:29:02,660 --> 02:29:06,370
但我从未…我从未想要你来
But I never...I never wanted this for you.

1691
02:29:07,740 --> 02:29:10,570
我工作了一辈子，我不会辩解…
I worked my whole life-- I don't apologize--

1692
02:29:10,580 --> 02:29:12,720
我照顾了我的家人
to take care of my family...

1693
02:29:12,910 --> 02:29:16,100
而且我拒绝当个傻瓜…
and I refused to be a fool...

1694
02:29:16,860 --> 02:29:21,880
随那些大人物的提线起舞
dancing on a string held by all those big shots.

1695
02:29:22,980 --> 02:29:26,690
我不会辩解，那是我的人生，但是我以为…
I don't apologize. That's my life. But I thought that--

1696
02:29:28,180 --> 02:29:34,070
等到了你的时代，你会成为掌握提线的人
that when it was your time... you would be the one to hold the strings.

1697
02:29:35,220 --> 02:29:38,450
参议员柯利昂尼
Senator Corleone.

1698
02:29:38,690 --> 02:29:40,830
州长柯利昂尼之类
Governor Corleone. Something.

1699
02:29:40,840 --> 02:29:43,270
另一个大亨[意大利语]
Another pezzonovante.

1700
02:29:44,030 --> 02:29:45,230
唉…
Well...

1701
02:29:48,630 --> 02:29:52,350
时间还是不够，迈克尔，时间不够
Just wasn't enough time, Michael. Wasn't enough time.

1702
02:29:52,890 --> 02:29:54,450
我们会做到的，爸
We'll get there, Pop.

1703
02:29:55,540 --> 02:29:57,010
我们会做到的
